WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.166 --> 00:00:01.700
Wake up, my lord

2
00:00:01.900 --> 00:00:05.000
Come on, sir, get the doctor

3
00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:07.566
And tear down this broken basement for me

4
00:00:07.800 --> 00:00:08.600
prince

5
00:00:09.266 --> 00:00:10.166
Lord, wake up

6
00:00:24.300 --> 00:00:26.766
Your Highness, you are always stubborn with me

7
00:00:27.600 --> 00:00:29.033
Why can't you be good?

8
00:00:29.100 --> 00:00:30.233
Young master

9
00:00:30.266 --> 00:00:31.666
The young grandmother's father is here

10
00:00:31.666 --> 00:00:33.300
He is clamoring to see you.

11
00:00:33.600 --> 00:00:34.966
Take care of the young lady

12
00:00:39.500 --> 00:00:41.500
Is there anything urgent about the visit of the father-in-law?

13
00:00:42.733 --> 00:00:44.133
Nothing serious.

14
00:00:44.133 --> 00:00:46.300
I just came to see you and Xiaoyan

15
00:00:46.533 --> 00:00:48.800
Then go back now that you've finished reading it.

16
00:00:48.800 --> 00:00:50.966
Didn't Xiaoyan tell you?

17
00:00:51.966 --> 00:00:52.766
Say what?

18
00:00:53.066 --> 00:00:54.833
Today, both of them are closed with me.

19
00:00:54.966 --> 00:00:56.633
What's clear

20
00:00:59.366 --> 00:01:00.500
What about money?

21
00:01:01.500 --> 00:01:02.633
8 million

22
00:01:03.533 --> 00:01:05.466
Since your daughter married into the Lu family

23
00:01:05.466 --> 00:01:07.400
You keep asking for a lot of money

24
00:01:07.400 --> 00:01:09.433
Today, it is 800 as soon as you open your mouth.

25
00:01:09.600 --> 00:01:12.400
What makes you think I'll give you a good son-in-law?

26
00:01:12.666 --> 00:01:14.466
You are wrong

27
00:01:14.466 --> 00:01:15.933
We are all family

28
00:01:15.933 --> 00:01:19.666
And Xiaoyan promises to get 8 million within three days

29
00:01:20.400 --> 00:01:22.100
He had a plan for you in the morning

30
00:01:22.100 --> 00:01:24.666
Yeah, did he forget to mention it?

31
00:01:24.666 --> 00:01:25.966
He not only did not forget

32
00:01:26.066 --> 00:01:28.866
He also took great pains to play a bitter problem with me

33
00:01:32.400 --> 00:01:34.866
Dad, why are you here?

34
00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:36.600
If father-in-law doesn't come

35
00:01:36.600 --> 00:01:38.600
How do I know I've been deceived by you again?

